title: Whitman Mission National Historic Site: Bird Lists
body: Bird Lists       The 2002-2003 Vertebrate Survey confirmed the presence, at least occasionally, of 202 species of birds in or near the park. These have been placed onto lists based on residency status and abundance. For definitions of the various residency categories or abundance categories see definitions.
